WEBVTT

00:02.870 --> 00:04.543
<i>ELIJAH: Over the course
of my long life...</i>

00:05.072 --> 00:08.817
<i>...I have come to believe that we are bound
forever to those with whom we share blood.</i>
<b><font color="#0A7C32">Ripped By mstoll</font></b>

00:09.510 --> 00:11.421
<i>And while we may not choose our family...</i>

00:12.179 --> 00:13.920
<i>...that bond can be
our greatest strength...</i>

00:14.815 --> 00:16.726
<i>...or our deepest regret.</i>

00:17.918 --> 00:20.990
<i>This unfortunate truth has haunted me
for as long as I can recall.</i>

00:26.260 --> 00:27.830
What do you make of that?

00:28.929 --> 00:30.203
No banner, no flag.

00:30.597 --> 00:32.167
Floated in out of nowhere.

00:32.766 --> 00:33.938
A miracle ship.

00:35.702 --> 00:37.272
Why is it just sitting out there?

00:39.339 --> 00:41.012
I suppose we ought to find out.

